{"ID":270296, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"296\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs295.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs297.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 296<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">my brother, my sister; and when they are by my side, I embrace them and they me.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">It is my meditation all the day, and more than my meat and drink,<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> to know how I shall make\n  the Saints of God<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> comprehend the visions that roll like an overflowing surge before my mind.<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"wideEllipse\">* * *<\/p>\n\n  <p class=\"std\">All your losses will be made up to you in the resurrection,<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> provided you continue faithful.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> By\n  the vision of the Almighty<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> I have seen it.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">More painful to me are the thoughts of annihilation than death. If I have no expectation of\n  seeing my father, mother, brothers, sisters and friends again, my heart would burst in a moment, and\n  I should go down to my grave.<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The expectation of seeing my friends in the morning of the resurrection cheers my soul and\n  makes me bear up against the evils of life. It is like their taking a long journey, and on their return\n  we meet them with increased joy.<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">God has revealed His Son from the heavens<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> and the doctrine of the resurrection<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> also; and we\n  have a knowledge that those we bury here God will bring up again, clothed upon<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> and quickened\n  by the Spirit<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> of the great God;<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> and what mattereth it whether we lay them down, or we lay down\n  with them when we can keep them no longer? Let these truths sink down in our hearts, that we may\n  even here begin to enjoy that which shall be in full hereafter.<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Hosanna, hosanna, hosanna to Almighty God,<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> that rays of light begin to burst forth upon us<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span>\n  even now. I cannot find words in which to express myself. I am not learned,<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> but I have as good\n  feelings as any man.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">O that I had the language of the archangel<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> to express my feelings once to my friends!  But I\n  never expect to in this life. When others rejoice, I rejoice;<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> when they mourn, I mourn.<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">To Marcellus Bates let me administer comfort.<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> You shall soon have the company of your\n  companion in a world of glory,<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span> and the friends of Brother Barnes and all the Saints who are\n  mourning. This has been a warning voice<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span> to us all to be sober<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> and diligent and lay aside<span class=\"footRef\">25<\/span> mirth,<span class=\"footRef\">26<\/span>\n  vanity<span class=\"footRef\">27<\/span> and folly,<span class=\"footRef\">28<\/span> and to be prepared to die tomorrow.<span class=\"footRef\">29<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"wideEllipse\">* * *<\/p>\n\n  <p class=\"std\">President Joseph Smith said: &ldquo;As president of this house, I<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108665\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108665)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108665)\">John 4:32<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108700\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108700)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108700)\">John 6:55<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110994\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110994)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110994)\">1 Ne. 14:12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114108\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114108)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114108)\">D&amp;C 58:54<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114404\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114404)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114404)\">D&amp;C 76:19-20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117127\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117127)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117127)\">JS&mdash;H 1:42<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112284\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112284)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112284)\">Alma 40:23<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112290\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112290)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112290)\">Alma 41:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113912\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113912)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113912)\">D&amp;C 46:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114727\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114727)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114727)\">D&amp;C 84:80<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115360\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115360)\">